docApp.directive('dusRelatedApplicationDtv', ['$timeout','$http','$compile','docCmmUtilFct', 'docCmmFct', 'docCmmLinkFct', function($timeout, $http, $compile, docCmmUtilFct, docCmmFct, docCmmLinkFct){
	return {
		restrict: 'A',
		link : 	postLink  //compile 이 등록되어 있으면 link 는 수행하지 않는다.
	};
	
	function preCompile(scope, elm, attrs, ctrl){
		/**
		 * 변수 초기화
		 */
		scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.dusRelApplParamVO.skey = scope.docVar.screenVO.skey;
		scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.dusRelApplParamVO.sortType = "DESC";
		scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.dusRelApplParamVO.pageNum = 1;
		scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.dusRelApplParamVO.pageRow = scope.docConst.REL_APPL_PAGE_ROW;
		scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.headerList = [
				                       		       {id:'chk', fieldNm:'', sortField:'', sortType:'', arrClass:''}   //check
					                       		     , {id:'ORG', fieldNm:'원문', sortField:'', sortType:'', arrClass:''}   //원문
					                       		     , {id:'STATUS', fieldNm:'유형', sortField:'ctry', sortType:'', arrClass:''}   //국가
					                       		     , {id:'AN', fieldNm:'출원번호', sortField:'appl_num', sortType:'ASC', arrClass:'ico_arralign ico_default', thClass:'tb_head_backcolor'}   //문서번호
					                       		     , {id:'AD', fieldNm:'출원일자', sortField:'appl_dt', sortType:'DESC', arrClass:'ico_arralign ico_default', thClass:'tb_head_backcolor'}   //일자
					                       		     , {id:'TI', fieldNm:'발명의 명칭', sortField:'', sortType:'', arrClass:''}   //발명의 명칭
					                       		];
		
		// 전체 카운트
		scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.pageCountVO.totRsltCnt = 0;
		// 전체 페이지수 
		scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.pageCountVO.totPageCnt = 1;
		// 보유 건수 : page 계산 위해 사용
		scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.pageCountVO.holdCnt = 0;
		// 미보유 건수 
		scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.pageCountVO.missingDocCount = 0;
		scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.pageCountVO.provisionalCount = 0 ;
		
		scope.findRelApplList = function() {
			var url = "../dus/findRelatedApplication.wips";
			var obj = { skey : scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.dusRelApplParamVO.skey
						, sortType : scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.dusRelApplParamVO.sortType
						, pageNum:scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.dusRelApplParamVO.pageNum
						, rowCount:scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.dusRelApplParamVO.pageRow
					  };

			$http.post(url, $.param(obj),{
				headers: {'Content-Type': scope.docConst.JSON_CONT_TYPE}
			}).success(function(data){
				scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.allChk = false;
				scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.maxChk = false;
				// 보유목록
				scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.rsltList = data.relApplTextList;
				
				//checkbox 초기화
				for(var i=0; i < scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.rsltList.length; i++){
					scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.rsltList[i].chk = false;
				}
				
				// Provisional of 목록
				scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.provisionalList = data.provisionalList;
				// 미보유 목록
				scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.missingList = data.missingList;
				
				// 미보유 건수
				if(data.missingList != null ) {
					scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.pageCountVO.missingDocCount = data.missingList.length;
				}
				// provisinal 건수 
				if(data.provisionalList != null ) {
					scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.pageCountVO.provisionalCount = data.provisionalList.length;
				}
				
				// 전체 건수
				if(data.relApplCnt != null ) {
					// 전체 보유 건수
					scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.pageCountVO.holdCnt = data.relApplCnt.totalRow;
				}
				scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.pageCountVO.totRsltCnt = scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.pageCountVO.holdCnt + scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.pageCountVO.missingDocCount + scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.pageCountVO.provisionalCount;
				scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.pageCountVO.pageNum = scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.dusRelApplParamVO.pageNum;
				scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.pageCountVO.pageRow = scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.dusRelApplParamVO.pageRow;
				
				// 전체 skeys
				scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.maxSkeys = data.skeys; 
				// 전체 페이지
				scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.pageCountVO.totPageCnt = Math.floor(scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.pageCountVO.holdCnt / scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.pageCountVO.pageRow) 
                + (scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.pageCountVO.holdCnt % scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.pageCountVO.pageRow == 0 ? 1 : 1) ;
				
				scope.clickDevBtnMarker();
				//scope.docQueryHighLighter($("form#paramForm :input[name=hl]").val());
				
				// 상세보기 오른쪽 메뉴 레이어 메뉴 수정
				if(scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.pageCountVO.totRsltCnt > 0){
					scrollRightSet("devRA", "Related Appl.");
				}
			}).error(function(data, status){
				/*if (/EgovBizException/.test(data.responseText)) {
		            alert(data.responseText.match(/EgovBizException: &quot;(.*?)&quot;/)[1]);
		            // error 처리
		        }
		        else {
		            alert("에러가 발생하였습니다. " + status + "\nError: " + data.responseText);
		        }*/
			});
			
		};
		
		/**
		 * 헤더에서 소트키 클릭시
		 */
		scope.relApplListSortUs = function(headerIndex){
			if(scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.dusRelApplParamVO.sortType === "DESC") {
				scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.dusRelApplParamVO.sortType = "ASC";
				scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.headerList[headerIndex].arrClass = "ico_arralign ico_arrup";
				//scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.headerList[headerIndex].thClass = "tb_head_backcolor font_color_orange";
				scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.headerList[headerIndex].fontClass = "font_color_orange";
			} else {
				scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.dusRelApplParamVO.sortType = "DESC";
				scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.headerList[headerIndex].arrClass = "ico_arralign ico_arrdown";
//				scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.headerList[headerIndex].thClass = "tb_head_backcolor font_color_orange";
				scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.headerList[headerIndex].fontClass = "font_color_orange";
			}
			
			scope.findRelApplList();
		};
		
		/**
		 * 이전페이지 클릭시
		 */
		scope.prevPageRelApplUs = function(){
			if(scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.dusRelApplParamVO.pageNum == 1){
				return;
			}
			
			scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.dusRelApplParamVO.pageNum = scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.dusRelApplParamVO.pageNum - 1;
			scope.findRelApplList();
		};
		
		/**
		 * 다음페이지 클릭시
		 */
		scope.nextPageRelApplUs = function(){
			if(scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.dusRelApplParamVO.pageNum == scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.pageCountVO.totPageCnt){
				return;
			}
			
			scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.dusRelApplParamVO.pageNum = scope.docVar.dusRelApplVO.dusRelApplParamVO.pageNum + 1;
			scope.findRelApplList();
		};

		/**
		 * Related Application Analysis
		 */
		scope.openRelApplAnalysis = function(skey){
			var url = DocCmmConst.US_REL_APPl_ANALYSIS_URL;
//			var url = scope.docConst.US_REL_APPl_ANALYSIS_URL;
			var form = document.createElement('form');
			$(form).attr('action', url)
				   .attr('id', 'relApplForm')
				   .attr('method', 'post')
				   .attr('target', '_blank');
			$(form).html('<input type="hidden" name="skey" value="' + skey +'" />' );
			document.body.appendChild(form);

			$(form).submit();
			$('form#relApplForm').remove();	
		};
		
		
	};
	
